p79
aVlaid out in ways that make sense for the particular situation.
p80
aVThey're usually all somewhat different.
p81
aVHere's my homework.
p82
aVAgain, numbers, words, laid out in ways that made sense.
p83
aVLots of calculations \u2014 we got really close to our calculators.
p84
aVIn fact, here's my calculator.
p85
aVFor Halloween, I went dressed up as a calculator.
