aa(lp89
VAt the beginning of each class, the professor would call on somebody
p90
aVto present the case.
p91
aVWhat they would do is they would explain what was going on
p92
aVand then dictate information that the professor would transcribe
p93
aVonto the many motorized blackboards in the front of the class,
p94
aVand then we'd have a discussion.
