aa(lp117
VMy father taught me about prototyping.
p118
aVHe showed me mock-ups
p119
aVthat he'd make to figure out the placement on the page
p120
aVfor the things for brochures that he was printing.
p121
aVAnd he'd use it to get feedback from customers
p122
aVand OKs before he sent the job off to the presses.
p123
aVThe act of making a simple, working version of what you're trying to build
p124
aVforces you to uncover key problems.
p125
aVAnd it lets you find solutions to those problems much less expensively.
